1
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:10,800
What can you do?

2
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,440
You can't even drive a car properly.

3
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:13,320
This is the last person

4
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:15,450
who has a recent large deposit record.

5
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:18,600
Gong Xiaoxia, 43 years old,

6
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,480
a housewife.

7
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,200
I guess she is the least likely.

8
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:24,000
So I put her last.

9
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:26,260
Guessing again? Who taught you that?

10
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:29,080
Well...

11
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:37,360
Who is it?

12
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:43,920
Police.

13
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:47,560
Ma'am, you don't need to be nervous.

14
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:51,160
We just want to ask you a few questions.

15
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:54,120
Didn't you make a new deposit yesterday?

16
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:54,920
40,000 yuan.

17
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:57,120
We want to know where it came from.

18
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,460
So your daughter left this money for you.

19
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,160
When did this happen?

20
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,240
It was the night before last.

21
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,960
I wondered why she didn't say a word.

22
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,690
Turns out she was running away.

23
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,320
That wretched girl.

24
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,400
She's deliberately trying to anger me.

25
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,380
Ma'am, please take a look.

26
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,860
Is this your daughter?

27
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,400
Where was this taken?

28
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,840
Why is she dressed like this?

29
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,900
Qianye Nightclub.

30
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,800
A nightclub? Impossible.

31
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:57,960
Understood. It seems she didn't tell you where she worked.

32
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,600
That's absolutely impossible.

33
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,240
My daughter has a proper job.

34
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,040
Then could you tell me where?

35
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,840
Guangnan Clothing Factory.

36
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,800
We had to pull strings to get her in.

37
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,180
The pay is pretty good.

38
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,960
Ma'am, do you know

39
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,560
who she's been in close contact with recently?

40
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:16,840
I don't know. She doesn't have many friends.

41
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,640
Oh, right.

42
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,600
I saw a guy who looked like a thug

43
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,840
drop her off once.

44
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,640
Ma'am, if she comes back,

45
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,560
you must tell us immediately.

46
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,520
I've screened

47
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,680
the most suspicious ex-convicts.

48
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,760
The files.

49
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,720
What files?

50
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,920
The files he gave you.

51
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,720
You mean the useless one?

52
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:50,300
Ma'am, please take a look and see if you recognize anyone here.

53
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:57,290
Sentenced to 5 years in prison by the People's Court.

54
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,720
This guy

55
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,980
was the hoodlum who brought her back.

56
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,240
Are you the boss here?

57
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,580
We're from the municipal CID.

58
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,160
Have you seen him?

59
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,360
Are you looking for him too?

60
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,400
I'm looking for him myself.

61
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,640
He borrowed a car from me last year,

62
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,520
hasn't returned it yet,

63
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,800
and is nowhere to be found.

64
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,960
When was the last time you saw him?

65
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,920
About three or four days ago.

66
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,720
What kind of car did he borrow from you?

67
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,600
A red Daihatsu minivan.

68
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,200
Alright, report your car as stolen.

69
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,400
You won't get it back.

70
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,600
Seriously?

71
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,480
Really.

72
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,640
Where does this guy usually live?

73
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,920
He lives right over there.

74
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:47,450
Let's go.

75
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:09,840
Boss.

76
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:13,500
Who does this person usually interact with?

77
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,600
I don't know, but he recently got a girlfriend.

78
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,200
She comes to him right after work,

79
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,000
and they go out after he changes.

80
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,360
Besides this female colleague looking for him,

81
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:22,960
do you have any impression

82
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:23,720
of two men,

83
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,440
one looking a bit slow,

84
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,840
and the other with fully dyed blonde hair?

85
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,040
Do you remember them?

86
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,160
You mean San'er and Xiao Wu.

87
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,840
It seems we

88
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,200
don't need to go to Guangnan Garment Factory.

89
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,120
You just came from there, right?

90
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,000
You found out too.

91
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,760
Let's exchange information.

92
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,600
Boss, keep an eye out for these two people.

93
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:00,000
If you find anything, you must notify us immediately.

94
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,520
Okay.

95
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:00,920
Okay.

96
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,600
Get out of the car.

97
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,800
Where are we?

98
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,720
We haven't even left Guangnan.

99
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,440
The boss told you to get out of the car,

100
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,520
so just get out.

101
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,660
Let's leave from the bus station.

102
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,440
We have checked all the people related to the suspect.

103
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:52,840
They must have left the city.

104
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,720
Look.

105
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:03,880
There are many rich customers in the nightclub.

106
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,840
If they directly rob these rich customers,

107
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:07,040
wouldn't it be easier?

108
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,040
Not at all.

109
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,480
Most of these rich customers have social backgrounds.

110
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,720
And once they lose contact,

111
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,520
their families will immediately report to the police.

112
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,280
But these girls in the nightclub are different.

113
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,760
Most of them are from out of town,

114
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,240
with no background and no backing.

115
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,280
They have low education

116
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,680
and are the easiest to be tricked.

117
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,040
They also rarely contact their families.

118
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,160
Once they disappear,

119
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,520
by the time we find the bodies,

120
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,450
how many useful clues will be left?

121
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,920
This Cao Aiyuan, alias Jiajia...

122
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,880
was to make money

123
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:33,440
to repay her mother for raising her,

124
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,640
and then leave the city without guilt.

125
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,320
The day after the incident,

126
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:40,120
Cao Aiyuan went to Guangnan Garment Factory and the dance hall to resign.

127
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,640
Her purpose was

128
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:44,560
to try to erase her personal identity information,

129
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,040
which we happened to run into.

130
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:49,970
She went home after leaving the dance hall and left the city that night.

131
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,360
But if they just wanted to rob money,

132
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,280
why did they have to kill them?

133
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:57,480
It's highly likely that there was an accident.

134
00:06:57,480 --> 00:07:00,480
Think about it. When they tied them up to extort money,

135
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,040
Li Na and Chen Zhaodi

136
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,440
had seen their faces.

137
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,360
If they let one of them escape,

138
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,680
it would be a hidden danger in the future.

139
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,640
And also,

140
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:09,320
these people were heavy-handed

141
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,240
and didn't follow any rules.

142
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:14,520
It's likely the girls were crying and trying to run away.

143
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,160
When they made a move,

144
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,480
they might have accidentally injured one

145
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:20,440
or accidentally killed one.

146
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,440
Could they spare the second one?

147
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,040
Since it had come to this,

148
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,640
both of them had to be killed.

149
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,420
Is there anything else to add?

150
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,850
Then compile this analysis into a report,

151
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,300
report the situation,

152
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,960
and apply for a nationwide arrest warrant.

153
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,220
We're here.

154
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,680
Thank you.

155
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,120
What's your name?

156
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,480
Cao Aiyuan.

157
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:33,600
Hey.

158
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,919
Why don't you ask me what my name is?

159
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:41,880
You are?

160
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,520
Hua Weihong.

161
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,810
That's so corny.

162
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,100
Just being polite.

163
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,240
I'm off.

164
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,250
I don't like other men touching me.

165
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,880
I know. I like it even less.

166
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:21,040
So this will be our last time.

167
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,820
Then you won't kill anyone this time, right?

168
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,240
I'm not a homicidal maniac.

169
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,480
Last time was an accident.

170
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,360
You saw it too.

171
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:37,760
If I hadn't stepped in, neither Lao San nor we could have escaped.

172
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:41,320
This time, once we get enough money,

173
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:44,640
we'll go somewhere no one knows us.

174
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:47,040
We'll start over, okay?

175
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,680
Did Nana recommend you?

176
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,040
Yes.

177
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:59,700
Sister Na said you took great care of her before.

178
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:02,010
So you were in this line of work before?

179
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,160
Yes.

180
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,240
What's your name then?

181
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,720
Azhi. Just call me Azhi.

182
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,440
Alright, Azhi.

183
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,880
Come to work tomorrow.

184
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:12,440
Okay. Thank you, manager.
